Cienciano live scores, players, season schedule and today’s results are available on Sofascore.

Cienciano next match

Cienciano will play the next match against Universidad Técnica de Cajamarca on Sep 13, 2024, 6:00:00 PM UTC in Peruvian Primera División.

When the match starts, you will be able to follow Universidad Técnica de Cajamarca vs Cienciano live score, standings, minute by minute updated live results and match statistics.

We may have video highlights with goals and news for some Cienciano matches, but only if they play their match in one of the most popular football leagues.

Cienciano previous match

Cienciano previous match was against Alianza Lima in Peruvian Primera División, the match ended with result 3 - 0 (Alianza Lima won the match).

Cienciano fixtures tab is showing the last 100 football matches with statistics and win/draw/lose icons.

There are also all Cienciano scheduled matches that they are going to play in the future.

This graph may help predict future Cienciano matches.
